{"tid":902430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【任性唔忍口】孕婦脂肪10cm厚難麻醉 生巨B成世高危","createTime":"2018-11-14T20:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T10:43:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"557bd38efe8b599f0d98e7bc83950ebd766a54d1","tid":902430,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T20:59:27.000Z","msg":"都是媽媽任性惹的禍？江蘇省淮安市一名嬰兒一出生就重達6公斤（13.2磅），幾乎是一般嬰兒的兩倍。負責接生的醫生指，嬰兒母親第一次產檢時，體重達88.7公斤（195.5磅），院方叮囑她要控制飲食，但她堅持我行我素，結果令胎兒一出生就出現呼吸困難等症狀，還一生承受高血壓、高血糖以及易患血管疾病的風險。<br />\n內地媒體報道，29歲產婦劉芬（化名）懷上第二胎16周首次產檢，體重已達88.7公斤，醫生同時查出她患有高血壓、糖尿病及脂肪肝。醫生當時轉介她到營養科學習控制飲食，但她並沒有去；隨後再見她時，她已懷孕約28周，但血糖偏高。醫生建議她運動以及調整飲食，並服用胰島素輔助，「但這人依然從性很差，我行我素，又沒來。」<br />\n直至這名孕婦出現不適，再到醫院求診時，她的體重已達100公斤（220.4磅），脂肪厚度達10厘米，若剖腹生產進行麻醉，有一定難度，對她和嬰兒都很危險，「正常剖腹生產只需一個麻醉醫生、手術時間25分鐘左右，但她用兩個，花一個多小時」。<br />\n嬰兒出生時體重約6公斤，不久便出現呼吸問題，只好轉科治療，幸好目前沒有大礙。醫生表示，胎兒在高血壓高血糖環境下生長，為將來罹患心血管疾病埋下病根，「這就是胎源性疾病。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181114/large/1542193489_d537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181114%2Flarge%2F1542193489_d537.jpg&h=e2bd7ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n29歲產婦產下13.2磅巨嬰，幾乎是一般嬰兒兩倍的體重。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181114/large/1542193489_78b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181114%2Flarge%2F1542193489_78b7.jpg&h=93361b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巨嬰出生後一度出現呼吸問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181114/58913037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181114%2F58913037&d=sIGfopfUIAdzml7A%2BFiBPtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=75c4f8b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181114%2F58913037&h=88b27100\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181114/58913037</a>"},{"pid":"74fab8155bcab4d7f4713b4558a802ddc0e0b525","tid":902430,"uid":80516,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T21:13:24.000Z","msg":"女權：你呢d係fat shaming，我鐘意肥就肥！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef95106b414a9420b488a2f0465deb9043feccc7","tid":902430,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T21:24:01.000Z","msg":"周街都係呢d大肚婆"},{"pid":"2bb8867e8e08585f32c79aad575b47e4daeb8043","tid":902430,"uid":63452,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T21:45:53.000Z","msg":"大家黃皮膚黑頭髮中國人嘛，駛乜聽埋班黃綠西醫講埋啲中醫無嘅概念，去搵朋友介紹嘅神醫調理下就無事<span style=\"font-size: small;\">儿</span>無事<span style=\"font-size: small;\">儿</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fe1d82264b912350cbbe5ae33a720629645fe6","tid":902430,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T22:54:59.000Z","msg":"身體自主。"},{"pid":"d6530a71c52dff5cb03bbd0de14b03e244aef60b","tid":902430,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T23:27:44.000Z","msg":"cargirl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084d6df4a372e04e4678eec9703ba78b816a0ba2","tid":902430,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T23:28:18.000Z","msg":"肥閪生仔正仆街"},{"pid":"3f7c56ef32b3565c53b38c64e2efeec80a3255fe","tid":902430,"uid":108038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6530a71c52dff5cb03bbd0de14b03e244aef60b","tid":902430,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T23:27:44.000Z","msg":"cargirl<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl